 />\n<br />\n2x^2-190 mod 3 = 0 for x&gt;9<br />\n2x^2 mod 3 = 1<br />\n<br />\nConsider (x^2)&bull;(2/3) 由於x係int (x^2)都係 但int&bull;2/3 唔會mod 1只會mod 2 所以唔成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申唔識數學proof 但我估咁解得通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"int*2/3 都有可能mod 1 eg. 302"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"呀 咁如果你將個x sub 3款數 ie x = 3n; x=3n+1; x=3n+2三次prove得唔得<br />\nx=3n嘅話2x^2一定always mod 0<br />\nx=3n+1嘅話2(3n+1)^2=18n^2+12n+2 所以always mod 2<br />\nx=3n+2嘅話2(3n+2)^2=18n^2+24n+8咁都係always mod 2<br />\n所以係冇可能？"},{"pid":"f2f134d519328296013bd1a6725e8a8479d89cc8","tid":2242883,"uid":365825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b205dcf7916a989f83da0248fd5af5db8ca8443","tid":2242883,"uid":67501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc4ab4a47c4c1c3e526776f5a4a86a2cbf18f2b","tid":2242883,"uid":365825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f0f43b50ffddf506578e8be10cf570aca4492f","tid":2242883,"uid":67501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"頂點嘅話y會係負數"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:14:46.000Z","msg":"咁咪prove到x係正數囉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"要同時係正整數 諗到R哂頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"唔會同時係非負整數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea268585e940f42a1c01b5890a2770a21185aa8","tid":2242883,"uid":45089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"2x^2 = 2 or 0 mod 3<br />\n3y + 190 = 1 mod 3"},{"pid":"35d5594d589afe6e64b2054f72198194d812420a","tid":2242883,"uid":37866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"let y= x+k<br />\n<br />\nby substitution k = 2/3(x^2+1) -64-x<br />\n<br />\nif there exsist a positive integer solution for both x and y,  k must be an integer<br />\n<br />\nfor k is an integer,  x^2+1 must be divisible by 3<br />\n<br />\nproof x^2+1 is not divisible by 3 (consider k=3m,  3m+1 and 3m+2) for positive integer m<br />\n<br />\nsince x^2+1 is not divisible by 3,  k is not an integer for all positive integer x<br />\n<br />\n應該大約係咁"},{"pid":"eb40ac4bc8a845b0fc516c7054323a9eed710ff3","tid":2242883,"uid":67501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位師兄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}